Subject: drm/i915/dp_mst: Account for FEC and DSC overhead during BW
 allocation
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 4e0837a8d00aa349910a73a6e14102f4c5d81ed5
